Nkechi Blessing has finally reacted to the footage of her working as security in America.
The actress, who is currently based in the U.S shared that she has been given a new position, while she shared a video of herself in a security uniform.
In the said video, the actress was seeing rehearsing her new role, while she made mistakes on what looked like a major road.
She wrote;
Anybody wey talk too much go collect, I don get security work for America ooo This hustle must pay.






